      <title>[Letter] 1821 May 24, Wheeling, Virginia [to] Miss Anne Jane Bell, near Nashville, Tenn[ess]ee / John Bell</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>The following document is a letter dated May 24, 1821, from Dr. John Bell to his sister Anne Jane Bell in Tennessee. John writes the letter to inform his family that he will soon be embarking on a journey to Nashville to visit them. He also discusses the other places and people he has visited and plans to visit.</abstract>
